Package com.adobe.aem.dermis.model

Interface IProperty

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAsset, ITypeAsset, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IOperationArgument
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Property, RestProperty, WSProperty
    @ProviderType
public interface IProperty
extends ITypeAsset
    Represents a property and it's metadata description. Property reside within a DataModel and can be used as keys for relationships between DataModel.

      • isMetadataKey

        java.lang.Boolean isMetadataKey()
